EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0800Z TO 1800Z DAILY 25 THRU 29 NOV
   WITHIN 23 MILES OF 57-35.2N 010-19.3W. VESSELS INTENDING
   TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL
   ON VHF CH 16 OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 291900Z NOV 13.
